young women better.

Summoner of the demon lord,
what is it that you desire of me?

Zaboeth led the demon race into numerous shrine raids, helping to diminish the gods' power for some time. However, most humans are unaware of this wicked demon's effect on the world. You dare awaken me?

I shall reward you with horror.

So you haven't noticed yet?

Would you like to see the

The dead are my guinea pigs.

During the end of the great war with the gods, he disappeared along with his extensive research facility. Records left behind state that afterwards, when the Imperial Army had been surrounded by the God Army, a being that resembled Shida appeared on the battlefield and destroyed all the enemies present in an instant. However, testimony from a knight who witnessed it all says that Shida murmured "I have found the materials I need for my new research. I shall be on my way." and then disappeared into the darkness.
dictionary.evolution:
This form is the result
of my research.
You wouldn't understand.

It still has an effect on me

I am a Dark Nymph-pune!
You are really interesting.
That's it! I will go with you-pune.

Thank you, Summoner.
For good or for evil,
use my power as you please.

I am a Dark Totem.

godly powers responsibly.

Huh? I was captured?
And I'm usually so good at
escaping... Oh well, be gentle.

dictionary.description: A rare being said to be magical and to have recorded the time when the gods created the world. It's of the metal record species. It's assumed to have much more experience than a Metal Ghost due to its bigger body. They don't belong to any one gender, but as their personality is more masculine, their speech usually earns them cold stares from women.

your side, right? Right!?

Feed me... growl rowl!
Work, magic, bright, gold, element.
Feed me something... growl grrr!

This may result in it granting a much more powerful effect than a normal Mimic when used as fusion material.

Delicious! Stinky! Ouch!
Meat, organs, blood, bones...
Get in my belly!

Blood will flow!

My wish has been fulfilled. I've

Ninjas must remain in the shadows.

dictionary.fusion:

I have my own hopes and dreams.

punishment I've been handed.
I have nothing to fear anymore.

I don’t want your kindness.

dictionary.evolution:
The power to control the dead...

You need of me, even though

There is no peace here.
That is why I must destroy all.
All can rest in peace then.

I will soon break at this rate.

Why do you appear before me?

Do you still desire to battle?

I like blood.

I want more blood...

lies dormant within this world.

However, this did not satisfy him, and he continued to collect divine weapons for research as he cut down the gods he met on the battlefield. Not much is known of the last stages of his life, but it is rumored that he lost his life to one of his own masterpieces. dictionary.evolution:
No! It's still not enough!

These blades are still not enough...

It seems my powers were sealed away

A world with order.

The reason behind their battle remains unknown, but the havoc that the siblings' fight brought about engulfed a multitude of demons, causing great destruction in Ishgria. Seeing no end to the fighting, the two brothers agreed to reconcile. However, the eldest had plotted against his little brother, sealing Aaron's powers into countless crystal shards that he scattered around Ishgria.

Give me more power. I must
become stronger than my brother

Compared to fighting,

I like your honest actions.

The world will keep spinning anyway.

He grew rapidly in strength and skill under his foster father's guidance, and it didn't take long for him to climb the military ranks. Upon clinching a battle royale victory, the king appointed Xenon as the commander of the royal army, entrusting the kingdom's safety to him.
dictionary.evolution:
There is no force stronger
than the desire to protect.
dictionary.fusion:
I have to hone my skills further.
Princess Estia needs my protection.
dictionary.summon:
I won't go easy on you
if you ever disrespect Princess Estia.
Not even if you're a Summoner.

dictionary.description: It is speculated that when the gods began their attack, King Radmuhl of Elysia was torn between putting up a fight or abandoning his kingdom. As the La Veda Republic fell to the power of the gods, unwilling to leave his throne, the king ordered his finest knight to take his daughter to safety, which Xenon dutifully did. However, neither of them expected that destiny had something else in store...
dictionary.evolution:
In times of peril,
the strength of one's soul
can do much more than his sword.
dictionary.fusion:
I have failed...
But I can't let that get me down!
As long as I exist, I'll grow stronger.
dictionary.summon:
I'll fight alongside you
if you promise to protect
Princess Estia, too.
